**Configurando NSG para database tier no compartment staging**

Para configurar NSG (Network Security Group) para o database tier no compartment staging, você precisará seguir os seguintes passos:

**1. Criar uma nova VPC (Virtual Private Cloud) no compartment staging**

```hcl
resource "oci_core_vcn" "vcn" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  cidr_block      = var.cidr_block
  display_name   = "vcn-staging"
  dns_labels      = ["staging"]

  # Configurar a subnetting
  subnets {
    cidr_block = "10.0.1.0/24"
    display_name = "subnet-staging-1"
  }
}
```

**2. Criar uma nova subnet no compartment staging**

```hcl
resource "oci_core_subnet" "subnet" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  cidr_block      = "10.0.1.0/24"
  display_name   = "subnet-staging-1"
  vcn_id          = oci_core_vcn.vcn.id

  # Configurar a segurança
  security_details {
    network_security_group_ids = [oci_core_nsg.nsg.id]
  }
}
```

**3. Criar uma nova NSG no compartment staging**

```hcl
resource "oci_core_nsg" "nsg" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  display_name   = "nsg-staging"

  # Configurar as regras de segurança
  ingress_rules {
    rule {
      protocol = "tcp"
      ports     = ["22", "3306"]
      source    = "10.0.0.0/16"
      target    = "10.0.1.0/24"
    }
  }
}
```

**4. Associar a NSG à subnet**

```hcl
resource "oci_core_nsg_association" "nsg_association" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  vcn_id          = oci_core_vcn.vcn.id
  nsg_id          = oci_core_nsg.nsg.id
  subnet_id       = oci_core_subnet.subnet.id
}
```

**5. Criar um resource Vault para armazenar as chaves**

```hcl
resource "oci_identity_compartment" "compartment" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
}

resource "oci Vault" "vault" {
  compartment_id = oci_identity_compartment.compartment.id
  display_name   = "vault-staging"
  encryption {
    key_type = "symmetric"
    key_id   = var.key_id
  }
}
```

**6. Criar um resource Cloud Guard para monitorar as atividades**

```hcl
resource "oci_cloudguard_aggregate" "aggregate" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  display_name   = "aggregate-staging"

  # Configurar as regras de monitoramento
  rules {
    rule {
      action = "ALARM"
      condition {
        type = "OCTET_COUNT"
        operator = "GT"
        value = "10"
        octets = "10.0.1.0/24"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**7. Criar um resource Cloud Guard para proteger a rede**

```hcl
resource "oci_cloudguard_policy" "policy" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  display_name   = "policy-staging"
  policy_name   = "cloudguard-default-policy"

  # Configurar as regras de segurança
  policies {
    policy {
      policy_name = "cloudguard-default-policy"
    }
  }
}

resource "oci_cloudguard_policy_attachment" "attachment" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  policy_id      = oci_cloudguard_policy.policy.id
  target_id      = oci_cloudguard_aggregate.aggregate.id
}
```

Essas são as configurações básicas para criar NSG, subnet, NSG, Vault, Cloud Guard e aggregate no compartment staging. Lembre-se de adaptar as configurações às necessidades específicas do seu projeto.

Para configurar a Security List para bastion host com network-segmentation no compartment Analytics, você precisará criar os seguintes recursos:

**1. Compartment Analytics**

Crie um novo compartment Analytics com o nome `LegalDoc-Manager-Analytics`.

**2. Data Source**

Crie uma data source para obter a lista de recursos no compartment Analytics.

```hcl
data "oci_identity_compartment" "compartment" {
  compartment_id = "ocid1.compartment.ad-1.139"
}

data "oci_identity_data_sources" "data_sources" {
  compartment_id = data.oci_identity_compartment.compartment.id
  filter {
    name   = "resource-type"
    values = ["data-source"]
  }
}
```

**3. Resource**

Crie um novo resource para configurar a Security List.

```hcl
resource "oci_identity_security_group" "security_group" {
  compartment_id = data.oci_identity_compartment.compartment.id
  name            = "LegalDoc-Manager-SG"
  description     = "Security Group para bastion host"

  ingress {
    description = "Ingress para bastion host"
    ip_permissions {
      ip_address = "0.0.0.0/0"
      value      = "allow"
    }
    tcp_options {
      protocol = "6"
      dport     = 22
    }
  }

  egress {
    description = "Egress para bastion host"
    ip_permissions {
      ip_address = "0.0.0.0/0"
      value      = "allow"
    }
    tcp_options {
      protocol = "6"
      dport     = 22
    }
  }
}

resource "oci_identity_security_group_rule" "rule" {
  compartment_id = data.oci_identity_compartment.compartment.id
  security_group_id = oci_identity_security_group.security_group.id
  description      = "Rule para bastion host"

  ingress {
    ip_permissions {
      ip_address = "0.0.0.0/0"
      value      = "allow"
    }
    tcp_options {
      protocol = "6"
      dport     = 22
    }
  }

  egress {
    ip_permissions {
      ip_address = "0.0.0.0/0"
      value      = "allow"
    }
    tcp_options {
      protocol = "6"
      dport     = 22
    }
  }
}
```

**4. Output**

Crie um output para obter a ID do Security Group.

```hcl
output "security_group_id" {
  value = oci_identity_security_group.security_group.id
}
